data.description: Spacious 4 Bedroom Cape Cod on a large level lot with Alley in rear.  Two bedrooms on 1st floor with hardwood, as well as in large Dining room.  The living/family room is off kitchen with a door leading to the patio & back yard.  The eat in Kitchen has oak cabinetry, gas stove & ceiling fan.  The 2nd floor has 2 bedrooms, (1 used as office), laminate flooring and a large cedar closet.  There is a full basement with laundry area & 2nd bath.  Refrigerator, Washer, Dryer, window treatments all convey, as well as desk & shelving in Kitchen & Family room.  1 year Home Warranty included.
